te>而家係要諗點解會咁 下面係我睇法<br />\n<br />\n1. 不反對通知書設終點響灣仔<br />\n2. 然後警方極順攤咁響灣仔阻一阻就徹退<br />\n3. 根本警方一早就預計大隊會繼續行到金鐘<br />\n4. 由得啲人去金鐘 入夜前唔會有行動<br />\n佔街都由得人佔 <br />\n5. 已經有電視台報道左港鐵會隨時會飛站<br />\n即係警方今次既行動唔係要驅散人群為主<br />\n反而係想困住人群唔比走<br />\n亦因為咁已經預早通知港鐵配合<br />\n6. 會封所有可以走既位 夜晚就會大規模拘捕<br />\n<br />\n我地要破解 就係唔好走入呢個局 或者係響佢行動前走左第二度 去一個唔會比佢地cut出入口既地區 呢個地方係銅鑼灣？尖沙咀？中環？呢樣野要現場在傾 但至少唔係佢地一早佈左局左<br />\n果個位置<br />\n<br />\n呢係係我小小睇法 天黑再出黎發夢 暫時現場既大家討論下先</blockquote>"},{"pid":"8c3ad62529f039070f4afbd65c3a9b3de16dfd96","tid":1337434,"uid":275109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T10:08:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b8524eb4396a96a29121d4bf3a0a877a7d2b75","tid":1337434,"uid":115866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T10:08:12.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"51ebea92106c2506557e756a16ab7e03dc08876b","tid":1337434,"uid":44174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T10:08:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cfa58d20984b2f67e99dec84d45422f4b7ddbb3b","tid":1337434,"uid":274000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T10:08:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4f60223cc8de8e97aaa0b6dac1376e249f6b2d88","tid":1337434,"uid":275109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T10:09:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff0186bf10b706acc0cc9a370bae39b9a03f3894","tid":1337434,"uid":250580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T10:11:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"af1ba3c1e1698a17aecee5e3e3df546a2fc70abe","tid":1337434,"uid":197563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T10:11:37.000Z","msg":"勿留金鐘"},{"pid":"2c9af503b57f77d8a83367e70cbbf5fcb331f570","tid":1337434,"uid":255816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T10:11:39.000Z","